      {
        "q": "How long does it take to generate a video?",
        "a": "Most videos are ready in 10-15 minutes. You'll receive an email when it's done."
      },
      {
        "q": "What photo works best?",
        "a": "Clear, front-facing portraits work best. The person should be clearly visible from head to waist."
      },
      {
        "q": "Can I use the videos commercially?",
        "a": "Yes! All generated videos are yours to use however you like, including commercial purposes."
